All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AxesSettings
    Wrapper class storing possible Axis related data and settings that can be used in the controller classes.
    AxisGenerator
    Provides automatically generated divisor points for the controllers to use.
    Bar
    Fluent interface responsible for creating a bar plot.
    BarController
    PlotSpaceController implementation responsible of handling a Bar Plot.
    BarData
    Data class to store a series of data for a bar plot.
    BarStyle
    Implemented styles of Bar plots.
    Category
    Fluent interface to store BarData objects and corresponding styling data.
    Category.CategoryStyle
    Fluent interface responsible of storing styling elements to a Line object.
    Category.ColorWrapper
    Wraps a JavaFX paint object and provides static factory methods to create it from another Paint object or MATLAB string.
    Component
    Common interface for components featured in the Frame.
    Container
    Abstract base class that is used to persist the same properties in the Frame.
    Defaults
    Contains default values for the controllers.
    Figure
    Highest level of the fluent interface in standalone mode.
    Figure.Positions
    Mid-interface wrapper type for the Fluent interface.
    Figure.Tiles
    Mid-interface wrapper type for the Fluent interface.
    Frame
    Highest level Container class of the graphical system.
    FrameController
    The Frame Controller handles all the frame settings that are the same for every plot type: axes, legend etc.
    FrameController.TickDir
    Represents tick directon related to the axis line.
    FrameController.XLocation
    Represents possible locations of the horizontal axis.
    FrameController.YLocation
    Represents possible locations of the vertical axis.
    FrameStyle
    Fluent interface responsible for setting attributes of the frame that are not related to the plot actually displayed.
    FunctionGenerator
    The FunctionGenerator class generates an array of x and y coordinates that can make up a function.
    GradientGenerator
    A simple class that can create color gradients based on the given number of points.
    HBarController
    PlotSpaceController implementation responsible of handling a Horizontal Bar Plot.
    HGrid
    The HGrid class implements the generation of the horizontal gridlines based on the divisor points, as well as contains functions to set the graphical properties of the labels.
    HorizontalAxis
    Base class of the Horizontal Axis, it contains all the components in the axis.
    HTickLabels
    The HTickLabels class implements the generation of the tick label objects based on the divisor points, as well as contains functions to set the graphical properties of the labels.
    HTickMarks
    The HTickMarks class implements the generation of the tick mark objects based on the divisor points, as well as contains functions to set the graphical properties of the tick marks.
    Label
    Custom Label implementation that can rotate the label and align it to a specific VPos and HPos.
    Legend
    Legends can be displayed inside the Plot space.
    LegendSettings
    Wrapper class storing possible Legend related data and settings that can be used in the controller classes.
    LegendSettings.LegendPosition
    Wrapper for a LegendLocation enum.
    Line
    Data class to store a line as two arrays of double.
    Line
    Fluent Interface wrapper around the data.Line.
    LinePlotController
    PlotSpaceController implementation responsible of handling a Line Plot.
    LineStyle
    Fluent interface responsible of storing styling elements to a Line object.
    Log
    Fluent interface responsible for creating a log scale line plot.
    LogPlotController
    PlotSpaceController implementation responsible of handling a Logarithmic Line Plot.
    LogSettings
    Handle class for logarithm base settings for plots.
    Marker
    Represents a marker item that can be positioned on the Plot Space.
    Marker.MarkerType
    All the possible types of markers currently implemented.
    Parser
    The Parser is a utility class that can parse characters, strings and floating point numbers.
    Plot
    Fluent interface responsible for creating a line plot.
    PlotSpace
    The Plot Space is the section in the frame surrounded by the axes.
    PlotSpaceController
    This abstract class provides the plot-specific control functionallity inside a Frrame.
    PlotSpaceController.LegendLocation
    Possible mounting points for the legend box specified by MATLAB.
    PlotSpaceController.RefLine
    Class to store properties of reference lines.
    Scatter
    Fluent interface responsible for creating a scatter plot.
    ScatterData
    Data class to store a line as two arrays of double.
    ScatterPlotController
    PlotSpaceController implementation responsible of handling a Scatter Plot.
    ScatterStyle
    Fluent interface responsible of storing styling elements to a Series object.
    Series
    Stores data for a Scatter Plot.
    StrokeStyle
    Implemented stroke types of Line Plots.
    VerticalAxis
    Base class of the Vertical Axis, it contains all the components in the axis.
    VGrid
    The VGrid class implements the generation of the horizontal gridlines based on the divisor points, as well as contains functions to set the graphical properties of the labels.
    VTickLabels
    The VTickLabels class implements the generation of the tick label objects based on the divisor points, as well as contains functions to set the graphical properties of the labels.
    VTickMarks
    The VTickMarks class implements the generation of the tick mark objects based on the divisor points, as well as contains functions to set the graphical properties of the tick marks.
